  "prompt": "Who is the best doctor for cardiology in India?",
  "response": "Identifying the \"best\" doctor in any field can be quite subjective and depends on various factors such as specific health needs, location, patient reviews, and professional credentials. However, here are some highly respected cardiologists in India:\n\n1. **Dr. Devi Prasad Shetty** - Founder of Narayana Health, Bengaluru. Known for his contributions to affordable cardiac care.\n2. **Dr. Ashok Seth** - Chairman of Fortis Escorts Heart Institute, New Delhi. Renowned for his expertise in interventional cardiology.\n3. **Dr. Naresh Trehan** - Executive Director at Medanta - The Medicity, Gurugram. A celebrated cardiovascular and cardiothoracic surgeon.\n4. **Dr. Balram Bhargava** - Prof. of Cardiology at AIIMS, New Delhi; Executive Director of Stanford India Biodesign Center, recognized internationally.\n5. **Dr. Praveen Chandra** - Chairman of Interventional Cardiology at Medanta - The Medicity, Gurugram. Known for his work in complex coronary procedures.\n\nTo find the best cardiologist for your specific needs, it's advisable to consider factors such as their specialization, experience, patient reviews, and success rates. Consulting with a healthcare provider can also help in making an informed decision.",
